LatexCommand ref
reference "seg.stats"

\end_inset

.
 This time series seems to be stationary, as the error-bars on the averages
 overlap, and the variance only changes by a few percent.
 The autocorrelation functions seem to agree within their error, but they
 are rather noisy.
\end_layout

